org.gephi.io.importer.api

Interface ContainerUnloader


  • public interface ContainerUnloader
    Interface for unloading a container. Gets graph draft elements and attributes. Get also basic params and properties which defined the content. Unloaders are used by Processor to load data from the container to the main data structure.
    Author:
    Mathieu Bastian
    See Also:
    Processor
